  <img src="/assets/img/projects/Cat Cafe/Cat Cafe Sketches 1.jpeg" alt="" />
  <img src="/assets/img/projects/Cat Cafe/Cat Cafe Sketches 2.jpeg" alt="" />
</div>
<p>
  After discussing with the event coordinator, we decided to merge the shelves
  concept with the spaced-out grid approach. This combination allowed for an
  airy composition and provided space for the elements and information to
  interact in a dynamic way.
</p>
