<p>
  I initially illustrated many elements, but my main concern was overwhelming
  the composition. Since this event poster needed to captivate a student
  audience at a fleeting glance, I decided to minimize the main illustrations. I
  leaned into a Bauhaus-inspired style, rather than the prominent mid-century
  modern look I originally envisioned, to achieve a cleaner and more impactful
  design.
</p>
